reviews.text: One of the best yakitori restaurants in town. Conveniently located in Causeway Bay.
Food was really really good but it’s quite pricy. Service was quite fast.
Very nice and authentic Japanese Yakatori. The ingredients are fresh and of good quality. Everything is perfectly grilled. A bit pricey but still value of money. Highly recommend fresh ginkgo.
Way overpriced and the food is far below average.
